<HEAD>Seven Somali Soccer Players Seek Asylum</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NAIROBI, Kenya (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Seven Somali soccer players, fearing they
will be forced into their nation's army, are seeking political
